mods.abstract: Two color window card (red and black on brown) announcing the Osborne Brothers at Club Seven Oaks on October 9. Poster features metal photoplates of the Osborne Brothers and of the sponsor, Martha White Flour Co. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/50236/
